<div id='communityQuestionsWithAnswers'>
<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/358459-what-do-you-think-the-mermaid-chair">What do you think the Mermaid Chair represents in this book?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_358459'><a id="like_count_community_question_358459" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/358459?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F6976.The_Mermaid_Chair">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/358459-what-do-you-think-the-mermaid-chair">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/358459-what-do-you-think-the-mermaid-chair">See all 2 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/54126590-almudena"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1592487931i/54126590._UX100_CR0,10,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/54126590-almudena">Almudena </a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Water is a symbol of emotion. The mermaid symbolizes being immersed in one's own emotions (water), becoming comfortable in one's mystical and emotional medium. 
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link802310" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=802310&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F358459-what-do-you-think-the-mermaid-chair%2Fanswers%2F802310-water-is-a-symbol-of">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
